# 🧠 ASTRO PROJECT FLOW + CONNECTION MAP

## 🌐 1. HIGH-LEVEL ARCHITECTURE

```
Browser Request
      ↓
src/pages/ (Routes)
      ↓
Layout System (BaseLayout.astro)
      ↓
Page Content (Home / Philosophy / Solutions / Contact)
      ↓
Reusable Components (UI blocks)
      ↓
Data + Content (services, markdown)
      ↓
Static Assets (public/)
```

