# 🧩 4. COMPONENT SYSTEM FLOW

```
components/
│
├── layout/        → global structure (Navbar, Footer)
├── home/          → homepage-only UI blocks
├── philosophy/    → philosophy page blocks
├── solutions/     → SaaS cards, service grid
├── contact/       → forms, contact UI
└── ui/            → reusable atoms (Button, Card, Badge)
```

### 🧠 Rule:

* `ui/` = reusable everywhere
* feature folders = page-specific
* layout/ = global skeleton

